Hi Alan,

Typically this is due to a fuel leak on the filler neck or the breather  
lines.

Richard Atwell hosts a most excellent diagram of the fuel system you  
can use to double-check your bus:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/FuelHose/09- 
FuelBreatherHoses.jpg

